        </uncertainty>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature value (Scown, C.D., 2011, Water Footprint of U.S. Transportation Fuels and supplying information of the article) (Vionnet, S., Quantis Water Database - Technical Report, 2012). </comment>
